### Test API Endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@correlationId = {{$guid}}

### 1. Create an Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{correlationId}}

{
  "customerId": "CUST-12345",
  "items": [
    {
      "sku": "WIDGET-001",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 29.99
    },
    {
      "sku": "GADGET-002",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 49.99
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Get Order by ID
# Ersetze ORDER-ID mit der ID aus Schritt 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDER-ID
X-Correlation-Id: {{correlationId}}

### 3. Create Payment (with capture)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{correlationId}}

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "amount": 109.97,
  "capture": true
}

### 4. Create Payment (without capture - only authorize)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{correlationId}}

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "amount": 109.97,
  "capture": false
}

### 5. Check OpenAPI Spec
GET http://localhost:3000/openapi/oms-openapi.yaml

### 6. Health Check (Docs)
GET http://localhost:3000/docs
